2-9}}\n* ''Black Dress Affair'' (2017)\n* ''Expelled'' (2017), with Emily Raymond\n* ''[[The Black Book (Patterson novel)|The Black Book]]'' (2017), with David Ellis, New York: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|978-1-4555-4267-3}}\n* ''The Store'' (2017), with Richard DiLallo\n* ''[[Juror No. 3 (novel)|Juror No. 3]]'', or ''Juror #3'' (2018), with Nancy Allen, New York: Knopf & Little, Brown and Company\n* ''[[The 13-Minute Murder (novel)|The 13-Minute Murder]]'' (2018), with [[Shan Serafin]], New York: Knopf & Little, Brown and Company\n* ''[[The First Lady (novel)|The First Lady]]'' (2018), with Brendan DuBois, New York: Knopf & Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|1-538-71495-7}}\n* ''[[The President Is Missing (novel)|The President Is Missing]]'' (2018), with [[Bill Clinton]], New York: Knopf & Little, Brown and Company\n* ''[[Unbelievably Boring Bart (novel)|Unbelievably Boring Bart]]'' (2018), with [[Duane Swierczynski]], New York: Knopf & Little, Brown and Company\n* ''The Cornwalls Are Gone'' (2019), with Brendan DuBois, New York: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|0-316-48555-1}}\n* ''The Inn'' (2019), with Candice Fox\n* ''The Warning'' (2019), with [[Robison Wells]]\n* ''Lost'' (2020), with James O. Born\n\n=== Short stories ===\n\n;Collections:\n* ''Triple Threat'' (2016), with Max DiLallo and Andrew Bourelle, collection of 3 novellas:\n*: \"Cross Kill\" (''Alex Cross'' series), \"Zoo 2\" (''Zoo'' series #1.5), \"The Pretender\"\n* ''Kill or Be Killed'' (2016), with Maxine Paetro, Emily Raymond, Rees Jones and Shan Serafin, collection of 4 novellas:\n*: \"The Trial\" (''Women's Murder Club'' series #15.5), \"Little Black Dress\", \"Heist\", \"The Women's War\"\n* ''The Moores are Missing'' (2017), with [[Loren D. Estleman]], Sam Hawken and Ed Chatterton, collection of 3 novellas:\n*: \"The Moores are Missing\", \"The Housewife\", \"Absolute Zero\"\n* ''The Moores Are Missing'' (2017), with Loren D. Estleman and Lee Stone, collection of 3 novellas:\n*: \"The Moo