-22423-9}}\n*# ''[[Cross My Heart (novel)|Cross My Heart]]'' (2013), New York: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|978-0-316-21090-4}}\n*# ''[[Hope to Die]]'' (2014), New York: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|978-0-316-21096-6}}<ref>{{cite book |last=Patterson |first=James |date=2014 |title=Hope to Die |url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_9780316210966 |url-access=registration |location=New York |publisher=Little, Brown and Company |isbn=978-0-316-21096-6}}</ref>\n*# ''[[Cross Justice]]'' (2015), New York: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|978-0-316-40704-5}}\n*# ''Cross the Line'' (2016), New York: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|978-0-316-40709-0}}\n*# ''[[The People vs. Alex Cross]]'' (2017), New York: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|978-1-780-89515-4}}\n*# ''[[Target: Alex Cross]]'' (2018), New York: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|978-0-316-27394-7}}\n*# ''Criss Cross'' (2019)\n** Others:\n*** \"Action\" (2014), with Brent Gargan, short story\n*** \"Cross Kill\" (2016), novella, New York: BookShots {{ISBN|978-0-316-31714-6}}\n*** \"Detective Cross\" (2017), novella, New York: BookShots\n* ''Ali Cross'' series:\n*# ''Ali Cross'' (2019)\n\n;''Travis McKinley'' series:\n# ''Miracle on the 17th Green'' (1996), with [[Peter de Jonge]], Boston: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|0-316-69331-6}}\n# ''[[Miracle at Augusta]]'' (2015), with Peter de Jonge, New York: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|0-316-41097-7}}<ref>{{cite book |last=Patterson |first=James |last2=De Jonge |first2=Peter |date=2015 |title=Miracle at Augusta |location=New York |publisher=Little, Brown and Company |isbn=0-316-41097-7 |url=https://archive.org/details/miracleataugusta00patt }}</ref>\n# ''[[Miracle at St. Andrews]]'' (2019), with Peter de Jonge, New York: Little, Brown and Company\n\n;''When the Wind Blows'' series:\n# ''[[When the Wind Blows (Patterson novel)|When the Wind Blows]]'' (1998), New York: Little, Brown and Company {{ISBN|0-316-69332-4}}\n# ''[[The Lake House (novel)|The Lake House